verses.text_plain: Hear my cry, O God; attend unto my prayer.
verses.verse_html: 1Hear my cry, O God; attend unto my prayer.

verses.text_plain: From the end of the earth will I cry unto thee, when my heart is overwhelmed: lead me to the rock that is higher than I.
verses.verse_html: 2From the end of the earth will I cry unto thee, when my heart is overwhelmed: lead me to the rock that is higher than I.

verses.text_plain: For thou hast been a shelter for me, and a strong tower from the enemy.
verses.verse_html: 3For thou hast been a shelter for me, and a strong tower from the enemy.

tokens.text: For thou hast been a shelter

verses.text_plain: I will abide in thy tabernacle for ever: I will trust in the covert of thy wings. Selah.
verses.verse_html:
4I will abide in thy tabernacle for ever: I will trust in the covert of thy wings. Selah. ▼
▼ trust: or, make my refuge

footnotes.body_html: ▼ trust: or, make my refuge

verses.text_plain: For thou, O God, hast heard my vows: thou hast given me the heritage of those that fear thy name.
verses.verse_html: 5For thou, O God, hast heard my vows: thou hast given me the heritage of those that fear thy name.

verses.text_plain: Thou wilt prolong the king’s life: and his years as many generations.
verses.verse_html:
6Thou wilt prolong the king’s life: and his years as many generations. ▼
▼ Thou…: Heb. Thou shalt add days to the days of the king
 , ▼
▼ as…: Heb. as generation and generation

footnotes.body_text: ▼ Thou…: Heb. Thou shalt add days to the days of the king
footnotes.body_html: ▼ Thou…: Heb. Thou shalt add days to the days of the king

footnotes.body_text: ▼ as…: Heb. as generation and generation
footnotes.body_html: ▼ as…: Heb. as generation and generation

verses.text_plain: He shall abide before God for ever: O prepare mercy and truth, which may preserve him.
verses.verse_html: 7He shall abide before God for ever: O prepare mercy and truth, which may preserve him.

verses.text_plain: So will I sing praise unto thy name for ever, that I may daily perform my vows.
verses.verse_html: 8So will I sing praise unto thy name for ever, that I may daily perform my vows.
